It is a Monitoring service to Monitor AWS Resources, as well as the Applications that run on AWS.
Host level Metrics consist of: CPU, Network, Disk, Status Checks.
It displays the metrics automatically about every AWS service that you choose.
We can create the dashboard to display the metrics about your custom application and also display the metrics of custom collections.

[Terms]
* Dashboards
CloudWatch is used to create dashboards to show what is happening with your AWS environment.
The dashboard has different 'widget type'.
* Alarms
It allows you to set alarms to notify you whenever a particular threshold is hit.
* Logs
CloudWatch logs help you to aggregate, monitor, and store logs.
* Events
CloudWatch help you to respond to state changes to your AWS resources.
